		"description":{
			"value":"<p><i>Set with the symbol of an upright gauntlet with an unblinking eye in its palm, this blade bursts into burning white light in the hands of one sworn to bring justice to the wicked.</i></p><p><b>Weapon</b><b>:</b> Heavy blade or light blade</p>\n<p><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Attack Rolls and Damage Rolls</p><p><b>Critical:</b> +1d8 fire and radiant critical damage</p>\n<p><b>Property:</b> <p>Paladins and avengers can use this weapon as an implement for paladin or avenger powers and paladin or avenger paragon path powers.</p></p>\n<p><b>Power (Minor Action)</b></p><p>The weapon casts bright light out to 4 squares until you end this effect as a minor action.</p><p><b>Power - Encounter (Immediate Reaction)</b></p><p>Trigger: You use this power when an ally adjacent to you is attacked by an enemy adjacent to you.</p><p>Effect: You switch places with the ally, and the target grants combat advantage to you until the end of your next turn.</p>",
